Click on the two arrows on the two ends to navigate your way through effects, overlays then borders. You could also press the speed-o-meter in the middle of the page. Choose your Effects. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e0/Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-3Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-3Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e0/Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-3Bullet1.jpg/v4-760px-Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-3Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

You can crop it, have extra effects, etc. by clicking on one of the buttons to the left of the speed-o-meter. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/69/Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-3Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-3Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/69/Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-3Bullet2.jpg/v4-760px-Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-3Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Once you have clicked on it, choose which category you want to browse. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/5e/Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-6Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-6Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/5e/Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-6Bullet1.jpg/v4-760px-Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-6Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Select which category you want. If you select one, it will be in your category's slide so you have to find it. It should be the last one. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/4f/Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-6Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-6Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/4f/Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-6Bullet2.jpg/v4-760px-Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-6Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Select the sub-category border etc. (make sure it has the film sign, which ever one's don't have the film sign will not be included) and then press okay. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/bd/Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-6Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-6Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/bd/Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-6Bullet3.jpg/v4-760px-Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-6Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

There you go, your border. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/00/Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-6Bullet4.jpg/v4-460px-Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-6Bullet4.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/00/Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-6Bullet4.jpg/v4-760px-Use-Pixlr%E2%80%90O%E2%80%90Matic-Step-6Bullet4.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
